comment.body: If they made Duke Nukem Forever, you can make anything no matter how late you are.

What is this? Looks a bit dodgy to me, but I'm a noob to ZN. If I run it directly on ZN it still makes request to clearnet and the account system (no ZN ID's) looks non-compatible with ZN. When I use it as a proxy server, it doesn't allow logins?
